Piedade!

302
00:37:08,260 --> 00:37:09,800
A postos!

303
00:37:09,970 --> 00:37:10,970
Preparar!

304
00:37:11,180 --> 00:37:12,260
Fogo!

305
00:37:56,470 --> 00:37:57,880
Todos vocês, fiquem aqui.

306
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:34,760
Nathan, Samuel.

307
00:38:39,550 --> 00:38:40,720
Margaret...

308
00:38:43,140 --> 00:38:45,680
